- [ ] Handoff note rendered from a lightweight HandoffDocument (summary + decisions + context pointers)
- [ ] Assistant profession `allowed_tools` updated to include `bring_in`
- [ ] Validation: target must be in caller's `handoff_to` list
- [ ] Session saved after handoff so state survives reconnects
